- Delete: scripts/state_machine.gd, scripts/enemy_state_machine.gd, scripts/enemy_grunt_state_machine.gd (after verification no refs remain).
- Verify: No state_machine calls/signals post-cleanup.

## Dev Workflow Rules
- Plan: Update .clinerules with features/decisions
- Implement: Follow established patterns (state machine, signals)
- Test: Debug prints, collision layers
- Document: Add lessons here
- Iterate: Small changes

